#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Micrometer and OpenTelemetry extension"
msgstr "Micrometer е’Ң OpenTelemetry жү©еұ•"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"ж— жі•дҝқиҜҒжӯӨжү©еұ•зЁӢеәҸзҡ„еҗ‘еҗҺе…је®№жҖ§еҸҠе…¶еңЁз”ҹжҖҒзі»з»ҹдёӯзҡ„еҸҜз”ЁжҖ§\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">йў„и§Ҳ</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This extension provides support for both Micrometer and OpenTelemetry in Quarkus applications. It streamlines integration by incorporating both extensions along with a bridge that enables sending Micrometer metrics via OpenTelemetry."
msgstr "иҜҘжү©еұ•еңЁ Quarkus еә”з”ЁзЁӢеәҸдёӯеҗҢж—¶ж”ҜжҢҒ Micrometer е’Ң OpenTelemetryгҖӮе®ғе°ҶиҝҷдёӨдёӘжү©еұ•дёҺдёҖдёӘжЎҘжҺҘз»„д»¶ж•ҙеҗҲеңЁдёҖиө·пјҢйҖҡиҝҮиҜҘжЎҘжҺҘз»„д»¶еҸҜе°Ҷ Micrometer жҢҮж ҮйҖҡиҝҮ OpenTelemetry еҸ‘йҖҒеҮәеҺ»пјҢд»ҺиҖҢз®ҖеҢ–дәҶйӣҶжҲҗиҝҮзЁӢгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This document is part of the xref:observability.adoc[Observability in Quarkus reference guide] which features this and other observability related components."
msgstr "жң¬ж–ҮжЎЈжҳҜгҖҠ xref:observability.adoc[Quarkus еҸҜи§ӮжөӢжҖ§еҸӮиҖғжҢҮеҚ—] гҖӢзҡ„дёҖйғЁеҲҶпјҢиҜҘжҢҮеҚ—д»Ӣз»ҚдәҶжң¬з»„д»¶д»ҘеҸҠе…¶д»–дёҺеҸҜи§ӮжөӢжҖ§зӣёе…ізҡ„з»„д»¶гҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This extension is available since Quarkus version 3.19."
msgstr "иҜҘжү©еұ•иҮӘ Quarkus 3.19 зүҲжң¬иө·еҸҜз”ЁгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[Micrometer Guide] is available for detailed information about the Micrometer extension."
msgstr "жңүе…івҖңMicrometerвҖқжү©еұ•зҡ„иҜҰз»ҶдҝЎжҒҜпјҢиҜ·еҸӮйҳ…гҖҠ xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[Micrometer жҢҮеҚ—] гҖӢгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The xref:opentelemetry.adoc[OpenTelemetry Guide] provides information about the OpenTelemetry extension."
msgstr "гҖҠ xref:opentelemetry.adoc[OpenTelemetry жҢҮеҚ—] гҖӢжҸҗдҫӣдәҶжңүе…і OpenTelemetry жү©еұ•зҡ„дҝЎжҒҜгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The extension allows the normal use of the Micrometer API, but have the metrics handled by the OpenTelemetry extension."
msgstr "иҜҘжү©еұ•е…Ғи®ёжӯЈеёёдҪҝз”Ё Micrometer APIпјҢдҪҶз”ұ OpenTelemetry жү©еұ•жқҘеӨ„зҗҶжҢҮж ҮгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As an example, the `@Timed` annotation from Micrometer is used to measure the execution time of a method:"
msgstr "дҫӢеҰӮпјҢMicrometer дёӯзҡ„ `@Timed` жіЁи§Јз”ЁдәҺжөӢйҮҸж–№жі•зҡ„жү§иЎҢж—¶й—ҙпјҡ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The output telemetry data is handled by the OpenTelemetry SDK and sent by the `quarkus-opentelemetry` extension exporter using the OTLP protocol."
msgstr "иҫ“еҮәзҡ„йҒҘжөӢж•°жҚ®з”ұ OpenTelemetry SDK еӨ„зҗҶпјҢе№¶з”ұ `quarkus-opentelemetry` жү©еұ•еҜјеҮәеҷЁйҖҡиҝҮ OTLP еҚҸи®®еҸ‘йҖҒгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This reduces the overhead of having an independent Micrometer registry plus the OpenTelemetry SDK in memory for the same application when both `quarkus-micrometer` and `quarkus-opentelemetry` extensions are used independently."
msgstr "иҝҷеҸҜд»ҘеҮҸе°‘еңЁеҗҢдёҖеә”з”ЁзЁӢеәҸдёӯеҗҢж—¶зӢ¬з«ӢдҪҝз”Ё `quarkus-micrometer` е’Ң `quarkus-opentelemetry` жү©еұ•ж—¶пјҢеҶ…еӯҳдёӯеҗҢж—¶еӯҳеңЁзӢ¬з«Ӣзҡ„ Micrometer жіЁеҶҢиЎЁе’Ң OpenTelemetry SDK жүҖеёҰжқҘзҡ„ејҖй”ҖгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*The OpenTelemetry SDK will handle all metrics.* Either Micrometer metrics (manual or automatic) and OpenTelemetry Metrics can be used. All are available with this single extension."
msgstr "*OpenTelemetry SDK е°ҶеӨ„зҗҶжүҖжңүжҢҮж ҮгҖӮ* ж—ўеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”Ё Micrometer жҢҮж ҮпјҲжүӢеҠЁжҲ–иҮӘеҠЁпјүпјҢд№ҹеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”Ё OpenTelemetry жҢҮж ҮгҖӮд»…йңҖжӯӨеҚ•дёҖжү©еұ•еҚіеҸҜж”ҜжҢҒжүҖжңүиҝҷдәӣжҢҮж ҮгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "All the configurations from the OpenTelemetry and Micrometer extensions are available with `quarkus-micrometer-opentelemetry`."
msgstr "`quarkus-micrometer-opentelemetry` жҸҗдҫӣдәҶ OpenTelemetry е’Ң Micrometer жү©еұ•дёӯзҡ„жүҖжңүй…ҚзҪ®гҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The bridge is more than the simple OTLP registry found in Quarkiverse. In this extension, the OpenTelemetry SDK provides a Micrometer registry implementation based on the https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java-instrumentation/tree/main/instrumentation/micrometer/micrometer-1.5/library[`micrometer/micrometer-1.5`] OpenTelemetry instrumentation library."
msgstr "иҜҘжЎҘжҺҘеҷЁдёҚд»…д»…жҳҜ Quarkiverse дёӯеёёи§Ғзҡ„з®ҖеҚ• OTLP жіЁеҶҢиЎЁгҖӮеңЁжӯӨжү©еұ•дёӯпјҢOpenTelemetry SDK жҸҗдҫӣдәҶдёҖз§ҚеҹәдәҺ link:https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java-instrumentation/tree/main/instrumentation/micrometer/micrometer-1.5/library[micrometer/micrometer-1.5] OpenTelemetry д»ӘеҷЁеҢ–еә“зҡ„ Micrometer жіЁеҶҢиЎЁе®һзҺ°гҖӮ"

