#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "API differences"
msgstr "API е·®ејӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The metrics produced with each framework follow different APIs and the mapping is not 1:1."
msgstr "жҜҸдёӘжЎҶжһ¶з”ҹжҲҗзҡ„жҢҮж ҮйҒөеҫӘдёҚеҗҢзҡ„APIпјҢдё”жҳ е°„е…ізі»е№¶йқһ1:1гҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "One fundamental API difference is that Micrometer uses a https://docs.micrometer.io/micrometer/reference/concepts/timers.html[Timer] and OpenTelemetry uses a https://opentelemetry.io/docs/specs/otel/metrics/data-model/#histogram[Histogram] to record latency (execution time) metrics and the frequency of the events."
msgstr "API ж–№йқўзҡ„дёҖйЎ№ж №жң¬еҢәеҲ«еңЁдәҺпјҡMicrometer дҪҝз”Ёи®Ўж—¶еҷЁ link:https://docs.micrometer.io/micrometer/reference/concepts/timers.html[пјҲTimerпјү] жқҘи®°еҪ•е»¶иҝҹпјҲжү§иЎҢж—¶й—ҙпјүжҢҮж Үе’ҢдәӢд»¶йў‘зҺҮпјҢиҖҢ OpenTelemetry еҲҷдҪҝз”Ё link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/specs/otel/metrics/data-model/#histogram[зӣҙж–№еӣҫпјҲHistogram] пјүжқҘи®°еҪ•иҝҷдәӣжҢҮж Үе’ҢдәӢд»¶йў‘зҺҮгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When using the `@Timed` annotation with Micrometer, 2 different metrics are https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java-instrumentation/blob/324fdbdd452ddffaf2da2c5bf004d8bb3fdfa1dd/instrumentation/micrometer/micrometer-1.5/library/src/main/java/io/opentelemetry/instrumentation/micrometer/v1_5/OpenTelemetryTimer.java#L31[created on the OpenTelemetry side], one `Gauge` for the `max` value and one `Histogram`."
msgstr "еңЁ Micrometer дёӯдҪҝз”Ё `@Timed` жіЁи§Јж—¶ link:https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java-instrumentation/blob/324fdbdd452ddffaf2da2c5bf004d8bb3fdfa1dd/instrumentation/micrometer/micrometer-1.5/library/src/main/java/io/opentelemetry/instrumentation/micrometer/v1_5/OpenTelemetryTimer.java#L31[пјҢOpenTelemetry з«Ҝдјҡз”ҹжҲҗ] 2 дёӘдёҚеҗҢзҡ„жҢҮж ҮпјҡдёҖдёӘз”ЁдәҺ `жңҖеӨ§еҖјзҡ„` `Gauge` пјҢд»ҘеҸҠдёҖдёӘ `Histogram` гҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `DistributionSummary` from Micrometer is transformed into a `Histogram` and a `DoubleGauge` for the `max` value. If service level objectives (slo) are set to `true` when creating a `DistributionSummary`, an additional histogram is created for them."
msgstr "жқҘиҮӘ Micrometer зҡ„ `DistributionSummary` дјҡиў«иҪ¬жҚўдёәдёҖдёӘ `зӣҙж–№еӣҫе’Ң` дёҖдёӘжҳҫзӨә `жңҖеӨ§еҖјзҡ„` `DoubleGauge` гҖӮеҰӮжһңеңЁеҲӣе»ә `DistributionSummary` ж—¶е°ҶжңҚеҠЎзә§еҲ«зӣ®ж Ү (SLO) и®ҫзҪ®дёә `trueпјҢ` еҲҷдјҡдёәе…¶еҲӣе»әдёҖдёӘйўқеӨ–зҡ„зӣҙж–№еӣҫгҖӮ"

